論男定女總有啲人唔爭氣<br />\n又要嘈但又想屌/比人屌<br />\n男既又要想睇自己條女有冇做雞 然後又想物色啲雞屌<br />\n女既就大家都知 又要做雞又要攞貞節牌坊<br />\n跟住又有班企撚晒喺道德高地既道德撚出黎話做咩屌人做雞 笑貧不笑娼<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">我屌你老味啦如果唔係有人開post講都唔知就黎全港女性都係有做雞呀 你班道德撚就等住幫啲雞埋單 幫人養便宜仔 用比人屌到爛既臭西當寶過埋下半世</span></span><br />\n<br />\n做雞係你地既選擇 但唔該做得出就唔好怕認<br />\n慢慢用埋餘下既人生點同你未來既另一半交代<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n到時唔好問點解比人飛 點解冇人要 因為係你自己一手一腳造成<br />\n呢個世界冇永遠收得埋既秘密 只有死心先守到秘密<br />\n各位兼職雞好自為之<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n熱門post引起社會關注<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 你以為自己邊撚個啊引起關注就攞住個keyboard出中環啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fc8f96b944595c19ce6f305d81d5dad8589f05a3","tid":212903,"uid":431,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-22T19:23:26.000Z","msg":"on撚9 post就一早開撚咗啦 依家先嚟wow<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"28c3ff96540ccaf5626f34e5e962fc53971a7498","tid":212903,"uid":431,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-22T19:24:01.000Z","msg":"季經扮新奇啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8ef5196d7d6405edc0d2ed8361c7def6b0ff06bf","tid":212903,"uid":13797,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-22T19:25:08.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>on撚9 post就一早開撚咗啦 依家先嚟wow<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"db26f9e06b322d39544bb362666596bbe9536747","tid":212903,"uid":21355,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-22T19:26:25.000Z","msg":"屌個個講啲嘢都差唔多 都開到十幾個po"},{"pid":"473623c179c59445aedb2f678bb5095778e1bd6c","tid":212903,"uid":431,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-22T19:28:17.000Z","